<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; margin: 2rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Install __APP_NAME__</h1>
  <p>This will install __APP_NAME__.app and configure system integration needed for local ENS and IPFS browsing.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>DNS resolver for <code>.eth</code> and <code>.wei</code></li>
    <li>Local HTTPS certificate trusted for browser access</li>
    <li>A command-line interface: <code>neomist</code></li>
  </ul>
  <br></br>
  <p>The installer will ask for Touch ID or password more than once because DNS changes and certificate trust use separate macOS authorization flows.</p>
</body>
</html>
